ExpressionPatternType

Supported expression types.

  • Inequality

    Works with Int/Float, e.g. x<5, x=3, x<4.5.

    Declaration

    Swift

    case Inequality = "ie"
  • InequalityExtended

    Works on Int/Float only, e.g. 4<x<10, 1<=x<18, 1.3<=x<15.4.

    Declaration

    Swift

    case InequalityExtended = "iex"
  • Regex

    Regular expression, e.g. [02-9]+.

    Declaration

    Swift

    case Regex = "exp"
